304
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:31,589
Regarde ailleurs.

305
00:21:42,040 --> 00:21:44,031
- Allô ?
- Mauvaise nouvelle.

306
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:46,270
Accouche. Je dois rentrer ?

307
00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:50,115
